  "instructions": [
    "Rinse the mussels under cold water and remove any broken shells.",
    "Heat the coconut oil in a donabe over medium heat.",
    "Add the galangal and sauté until fragrant, about 1 minute.",
    "Add the mussels, fish sauce, lime juice, chili flakes, and sugar. Stir to combine.",
    "Add the coconut milk and bring the mixture to a simmer.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and cook, covered, until the mussels are cooked through, about 5 minutes.",
    "Stir in the green onions, cilantro, bell peppers, and Thai basil.",
    "Season with salt to taste.",
    "Serve the mussel mixture hot over a bed of mixed greens, garnished with additional green onions and cilantro if desired."
  ],
